title.en: Okazari Tsuma wa Reikoku Danna-sama to Rien Shitai!
Himegimi wa Wakaki Shougun ni Oboreru
Akuyaku Reijou wa Danna-sama to Rien ga Shitai!
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Ryuujin-sama to Miko Hanayome no Chigiri
Doku-suki Reijou wa Kekkon ni Tadoritsukai
Danna-sama ga Chicchai Mofumofu ni narimashita ~Watashi wo Akujo da to Gokai shiteita no ni, Subete Gibo no Uso da to Kizuita you desu~
Furin Aite ga Mama Haha Datta no de Rien wo Keikaku Itashimasu
Ookami Heika no Shitsukekata - Akuyaku Reijou wa Hametsu Flag to Ichiya wo Tomoni shite Shimattakedo, Dekiaisasemasu!
Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
Hameraremashita ga, Shiawase ni narimashita - Kizumono Reijou to Hidamari no Madoushi
Kurokishi-sama kara Zenryoku de Dekiaisareteimasu ga, Sugomori Seijo wa Kyou mo Hikikomoritai!
Uchi no Outaishi Denka wa Kyou mo Gu Kawaii ~Konyaku Haki desu no? Mochiron Kyakkashimasu keredo, Riyuu wa Kiite Sashiagemasu wa~
Meryoku no nai Otaku Reijou wa, Jiki Koushaku-sama no Ichizu na Dekiai ni Honrousareru
